flowchart TD
    A[Question + Schema Key] --> B[Schema Normalization\nAlias Mapping + Prompt Cleanup]
    B --> C[Expected Type Resolver]

    C -->|boolean| D1[Boolean Intent Rewrite\nYes/No + Evidence Prompt]
    C -->|date| D2[Date-Specific Output Constraints]
    C -->|numeric\namount/rate/ratio/delta| D3[Numeric Output Constraints]
    C -->|text| D4[Text/Entity Constraints\nCOMPANYNAME guardrails]

    D1 --> E[Primary Model Call]
    D2 --> E
    D3 --> E
    D4 --> E

    E --> F{Output Looks Malformed\nfor Expected Type?}

    F -->|Yes: numeric/date got bool-like| G1[Typed Retry #1\nforce concrete typed value]
    G1 --> G2{Still malformed?}
    G2 -->|Yes| G3[Typed Retry #2]
    G2 -->|No| H
    G3 --> H

    F -->|Yes: text got bool/number/noise| T1[Text Retry #1]
    T1 --> T2{Still malformed?}
    T2 -->|Yes| T3[Strict Text Retry #2]
    T2 -->|No| H
    T3 --> H

    F -->|No| H[Prepare Prediction for Scoring\nType-specific extraction]

    H --> I[Type-Aware Evaluation]
    I --> I1[Boolean: normalize Yes/No/1/0]
    I --> I2[Date: normalize to ISO]
    I --> I3[Numeric: entity/primary-value match]
    I --> I4[Text: token + semantic checks]

    I --> J[Source-Span Coercion\nFind verbatim evidence span]
    J --> K[Final Metrics + Frame Output]

    classDef imp fill:#0f2b46,stroke:#55b1ff,color:#eaf6ff,stroke-width:1.2px;
    classDef core fill:#1f2937,stroke:#9ca3af,color:#f9fafb,stroke-width:1px;
    class C,D1,D2,D3,D4,G1,G3,T1,T3,I,J imp;
    class A,B,E,F,H,K core;
